  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nChat platform success is in network effects. The user referral program rewards Android users for bringing their friends and family into Status. 100 SNT to the referrer for each new user who creates an account.\r\n\r\nApp store rules prevent us from being able to offer this scheme on iOS.\r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\n\r\n3 separate entry points for the invite flow:\r\n- From app intro screen, [in existing `Invite Friends` bubble](https://www.figma.com/file/aS1ct66VQ6V0cio7vSqS8UoG/Chat?node-id=8738%3A128)\r\n- From [the `+` menu in chat section](https://www.figma.com/file/aS1ct66VQ6V0cio7vSqS8UoG/Chat?node-id=8738%3A295)\r\n- As [an empty state](https://www.figma.com/file/aS1ct66VQ6V0cio7vSqS8UoG/Chat?node-id=12%3A127) on the `Profile` > `Contacts` screen, `Start group chat` flow, and `Start new chat flow`\r\n\r\nPast the entry point, there are three more steps:\r\n- https://www.figma.com/file/aS1ct66VQ6V0cio7vSqS8UoG/Chat?node-id=8738%3A597\r\n- [User invites someone out of app](https://www.figma.com/file/aS1ct66VQ6V0cio7vSqS8UoG/Chat?node-id=8738%3A1064)\r\n- [Confirmation screen displayed](https://www.figma.com/file/aS1ct66VQ6V0cio7vSqS8UoG/Chat?node-id=8738%3A435)\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n- Please match [Figma designs](https://www.figma.com/file/aS1ct66VQ6V0cio7vSqS8UoG/Chat?node-id=12%3A127)\r\n\r\n## Notes\r\n\r\nAre there any steps missing from code perspective?\r\nWhen is account creation by another user actually confirmed? Once user generates a key?",
